snippet.title: Rusty Lake Hotel Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome our guests to the Rusty Lake Hotel and make sure they will have a pleasant stay. There will be 5 dinners this week. Make sure every dinner is worth dying for...

A single, one way trip to this undiscovered part in the Rusty Lake universe will cost only $ 1,99 / € 1,99 and is now available on:

iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1059911569
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.RustyLake.RustyLakeHotel
Desktop (Windows/Mac): 
http://store.steampowered.com/app/435120/
http://rustylake.itch.io/rustylakehotel

Rusty Lake Hotel is a mysterious point and click game developed by the creators of the Cube Escape series. 

We will unfold the Rusty Lake story one step at a time. So check RustyLake.com every day for new content!

Like and follow:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/rustylakecom
Twitter: https://twitter.com/rustylakecom
And subscribe to our mailing list: http://eepurl.com/bhphw1
